00:07:27.920 --> 00:07:30.720
<i>What you see here is
the transformation of a rhinoceros beetle.</i>

00:07:30.720 --> 00:07:34.140
<i>Wow, it's already started
to transform, professor!</i>

00:07:34.140 --> 00:07:38.970
