fees and interest anymore.

00:09:26.960 --> 00:09:28.790
So you were cheated?

00:09:29.670 --> 00:09:30.920
In any case,

00:09:30.920 --> 00:09:33.210
the shop closes today.

00:09:33.920 --> 00:09:36.380
Why don't you go
to the police for help?

