if you can't repay your debt, right?

00:10:40.490 --> 00:10:43.280
Hey! Do you know where
to find Niya Niya Loan?

00:10:43.280 --> 00:10:45.290
Huh, you need a loan or somethin'?

00:10:45.290 --> 00:10:47.750
