00:12:15.710 --> 00:12:17.460
I'm a hero for fun.

00:12:19.670 --> 00:12:22.050
Really? Keep at it, then.

00:12:22.550 --> 00:12:24.180
Wait, did you say hero?

00:12:25.180 --> 00:12:27.010
